keymaps.name: Colemak DH
keymaps.description: Colemak is based on QWERTY, but it places the most frequent letters under the strongest fingers. This is the PC version.

keymaps.name: QWERTY
keymaps.description: QWERTY is the mother of all layouts. This is the PC version.

macroActions.command:
set module.trackpoint.baseSpeed 0.25
set module.trackpoint.speed 0.8
set module.trackpoint.xceleration 1.8
set module.keycluster.scrollAxisLock 1
set module.trackpoint.navigationMode.mod scroll
set module.trackpoint.navigationMode.shift caret
set diagonalSpeedCompensation 1
set macroEngine.extendedCommands 1

setLedTxt 0 QRZ
set module.trackpoint.navigationMode.shift cursor
set module.trackpoint.navigationMode.base cursor
set module.trackpoint.navigationMode.fn scroll
